      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "だけど、この間のデートの後は\nカメラの向こうにいる人を意識するようにしたんです",
      "startTime": 57.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "カメラマンさんやこのグラビアを見る人が\n照れて顔が赤くなっちゃうようにしようって！",
      "startTime": 64.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
