      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "それで手応えが掴めて、だんだんと他の人も\n意識出来るようになった……って感じです",
      "startTime": 84.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか。嬉しいけど、結構恥ずかしいな……\nあとデートじゃないからな。みんなに変に思われるだろ",
      "startTime": 93.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
